OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS to introduce Martha's  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frule in hospitals          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The health secretary is backing the    
OL,6, introduction of "Martha's Rule", to    
OL,7, ensure hospital patients know they have
OL,8, the right to a second opinion, and NHS 
OL,9, England will begin work to action it.  
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Steve Barclay met Merope 
OL,12,FMills, who had raised concerns with    
OL,13,Fdoctors about her daughter's treatment.
OL,15,FMartha, 13, had been admitted to       
OL,16,Fhospital after falling off her bike.   
OL,18,FAn injury to her pancreas was serious  
OL,19,Fbut survivable. Within days, however,  
OL,20,Fshe had died of sepsis.                
